      {
        "question": " Is the CT triple phase liver scan painful?",
        "answer": "No. You’ll feel a warm flush when the contrast enters, but no pain.\n"
      },
      {
        "question": "How long does the entire appointment take?",
        "answer": "From check-in to discharge: **45–60 minutes**; scan itself: 10–15 minutes."
      },
      {
        "question": "Can I drive home after the scan?",
        "answer": "Yes, unless you took a sedative (rare). There are no lingering effects.\n"
      },
      {
