      "title": " CT Triple Phase Liver Scan – Advanced Imaging at Cadabams Diagnostics",
      "description": " Get a fast, low-dose CT Triple Phase Liver scan at Cadabams Diagnostics Bangalore. Detect tumors, cirrhosis & lesions early. Same-day results. Book now.\n",
